<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Garreth Lawbringer</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-04-24 03:54:09</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Hello All,<BR>
   Now that I own one of these sweet caster beating sticks, I'd like to share how I aquired the item.  Morty spawns in the Undead Valley in the Rathe Mts, take the 1st left after zoneing in from feerot.<BR>
    When you get to the valley, you will come across a lizard camp----now kill every lizard and wanderer(basilisks, lizards, fire beetles) in the area.  It was myself (lvl 40 shaman at time) and a lvl 45 Ranger clearing the area.  About 4 hrs into the camp Morty Spawned.<BR>
     I know for a fact that Morty spawns more than once a week as another lucky shaman got his staff on same day(was making my SOW potion runs)<BR>
     The key is to keep clearing the area around the lizard camp, and fyi brother Z was up the whole time we were waiting on Morty.<BR>
<BR>
   Hope this clears up some confusion,<BR>
   <BR>
     Garreth<BR>
<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
