<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Hello guys, here is the scoop. Morti is around lvl 35 to 40 as <BR>
you already seem to know. Read about it at www.eqshaman.com or just let <BR>
me tell you.  Me and orge warrior friend walked up to our long awaiting<BR>
camp.  In the 1 3 mins he spawned but we didn't get kill ucz he waxed us<BR>
and our lvl 40 mage wasn't there yet.  Some other guys got him.  He spawns<BR>
at a point at the bottom of a heel.  From ferrot take 1 left, its not to far. It opens up<BR>
at the other end to hg valle where the you can take a left to the spinx or stay in hg<BR>
valley..Don't go to neither.  Stay around the 2 haunt spots, and lizzy and orc camp.  he spawns<BR>
a little of the lizzy camp.  I camped him 12 to 16 hours forcing spawn and got him.  Other  tiems like<BR>
on a busy sunday.  I have seen him up to 5 times in one day.  Its all about killing the right wandering lizzys<BR>
yet I do not know which. Just shout and ask people to "plz kill any wandering lizzys" and maybe a few<BR>
of them might which is bettar than none. Just kill anything in that area.  Also morti seems to run<BR>
the same rout as that monk npc high taling it all over the place.</font></td></tr></table>
